<a class="gotop anchor" href="#ref_[1]_78414" id="refIndex_1_78414" name="refIndex_1_78414" title="向上跳转">  </a>
<a class="text" href="/reference/1417068/cc27qbvumifhoCaRiaKHbBTl2oxnyzIRzfAC_gORlB3mOmcn0an9va7BBrzkdKdzH8h8Bktb65BsQQDlZRVuTX5Yi4RZXnSdjSenrx9gkxjJPsGq8ke1JAsmPQ" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">音乐旋律<span class="linkout"> </span></a>
<span class="site">．中国音乐网</span><span>[引用日期2013-05-07]</span></li></ul>
</dd>
</dl>
